summary:
- Stress analysis of offshore/onshore piping systems.
- Stress analysis of FRP piping.
- Static analysis for Underground Piping.
- Static analysis for two phase flow slug lines.
- Stress analysis of lines connected to pumps,centrifugal compressor, pressure vessels,Steam Turbines,Column Re- boilers, storage tanks, shell & tube heat exchangers, columns, relief valve, flare header system and rack piping.
- Flexibility analysis of well head lines containing well head movements for HP-HT piping systems.
- Flexibility analysis of riser, bridge lines, pig launcher system with relative platform and bridge movements.
- Familiar with International coeds ASME B31.3, ASME Sec.VIII Div.1 &2, EN13480, EN13445, RToD, NEN 3650, API610, API 617, API661, DNV.
- Flange leakage check as per Equivalent Pressure method ,ASME VIII Div.1, App.2 and NC-3658.3 methods.
- Flange leakage check as per EN1591 for large diameter DIN flanges.
- Study of Stress concentration on Equipment Nozzles using WRC 107,WRC 297
- Support type selection & preparation support MTO.
- Engineering checking of pipe support drawings.
- Preparation of critical line list.
- Preparing Specification for Spring Hanger,Expansion Joints.

Specialties: CAESAR II, PV Elite, VES, PCC, Rohr2, DIMy, Smart Plant Review, Navisworks,Autodesk Design Review, FE Pipe, Nozzle Pro, AutoCAD 2019, Plant 3D, PDMS
